---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="SSS – AsistanApp" 
  description="AsistanApp hakkında sık sorulan sorular. Yapay zeka asistan, fiyatlandırma, güvenlik ve teknik destek."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero section-sm observe-animation" style="background: var(--bg-accent);">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1 class="animate-fade-in-up" style="font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);">
        <span data-i18n="tr">Sık Sorulan Sorular</span>
        <span data-i18n="en">Frequently Asked Questions</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted animate-fade-in-up" style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; animation-delay: 0.2s; opacity: 0;">
        <span data-i18n="tr">AsistanApp hakkında merak ettiklerinizin yanıtları</span>
        <span data-i18n="en">Answers to your questions about AsistanApp</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Content -->
  <section class="section observe-animation">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      
      <!-- General Questions -->
      <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10);">
        <h2 style="font-size: var(--font-size-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-6); text-align: center; color: var(--primary);">
          <span data-i18n="tr">🤖 Genel Sorular</span>
          <span data-i18n="en">🤖 General Questions</span>
        </h2>
        
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3);">
          <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up" style="padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); color: var(--primary); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">❓ AsistanApp nedir?</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">❓ What is AsistanApp?</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">Yapay zeka ile müşterilerinizle WhatsApp, Instagram, Web ve telefon üzerinden 7/24 konuşan otomatik asistan platformu.</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">AI assistant platform that talks to your customers 24/7 via WhatsApp, Instagram, Web and phone.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up" style="padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); color: var(--primary); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">⚡ Nasıl çalışır?</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">⚡ How does it work?</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">Şirketinizin verilerini öğrenir, müşteri sorularını yanıtlar, satış yapar ve randevu alır.</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">Learns your company data, answers customer questions, makes sales and books appointments.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up" style="padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); color: var(--primary); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">🔧 Kurulum ne kadar sürer?</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">🔧 How long does setup take?</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">Temel kurulum 1-2 gün, özelleştirme 1 hafta içinde tamamlanır.</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">Basic setup takes 1-2 days, customization completed within 1 week.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Pricing Questions -->
      <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10);">
        <h2 style="font-size: var(--font-size-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-6); text-align: center; color: var(--primary);">
          <span data-i18n="tr">💰 Fiyatlandırma</span>
          <span data-i18n="en">💰 Pricing</span>
        </h2>
        
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3);">
          <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up" style="padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); color: var(--primary); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">💳 Hangi ödeme yöntemleri kabul ediliyor?</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">💳 What payment methods are accepted?</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">Kredi kartı, havale/EFT ve kurumsal fatura seçenekleri mevcuttur.</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">Credit card, bank transfer and corporate invoice options available.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up" style="padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); color: var(--primary); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">📊 Plan değişikliği yapabilir miyim?</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">📊 Can I change plans?</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">Evet, istediğiniz zaman planınızı yükseltebilir veya düşürebilirsiniz.</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">Yes, you can upgrade or downgrade your plan anytime.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up" style="padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); color: var(--primary); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">🎁 Ücretsiz deneme var mı?</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">🎁 Is there a free trial?</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">Lansmanımızda 14 günlük ücretsiz deneme sunacağız.</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">We will offer a 14-day free trial at launch.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Technical Questions -->
      <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10);">
        <h2 style="font-size: var(--font-size-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-6); text-align: center; color: var(--primary);">
          <span data-i18n="tr">🔒 Teknik & Güvenlik</span>
          <span data-i18n="en">🔒 Technical & Security</span>
        </h2>
        
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3);">
          <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up" style="padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); color: var(--primary); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">🛡️ Verilerim güvende mi?</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">🛡️ Is my data safe?</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">Evet, KVKK/GDPR uyumlu, SSL şifreli ve ISO 27001 standartlarında koruyoruz.</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">Yes, KVKK/GDPR compliant, SSL encrypted and protected with ISO 27001 standards.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up" style="padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); color: var(--primary); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">🌐 Hangi dilleri destekliyor?</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">🌐 Which languages are supported?</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">Türkçe ve İngilizce temel, Enterprise planında 50+ dil desteği.</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">Turkish and English basic, 50+ languages support in Enterprise plan.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up" style="padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); color: var(--primary); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">📱 Hangi platformları destekliyor?</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">📱 Which platforms are supported?</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook Messenger, Web widget ve telefon sistemi.</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook Messenger, Web widget and phone system.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Support Questions -->
      <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
        <h2 style="font-size: var(--font-size-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-6); text-align: center; color: var(--primary);">
          <span data-i18n="tr">🎯 Destek & Eğitim</span>
          <span data-i18n="en">🎯 Support & Training</span>
        </h2>
        
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-3);">
          <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up" style="padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); color: var(--primary); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">📞 Teknik destek nasıl alırım?</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">📞 How do I get technical support?</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">7/24 canlı destek, e-posta ve telefon ile ulaşabilirsiniz.</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">24/7 live support, email and phone contact available.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up" style="padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); color: var(--primary); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">🎓 Eğitim sağlanıyor mu?</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">🎓 Is training provided?</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">Evet, ücretsiz kurulum eğitimi ve video kılavuzlar sağlıyoruz.</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">Yes, we provide free setup training and video guides.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up" style="padding: var(--space-4);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); color: var(--primary); font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">🚀 Ne zaman başlayabilirim?</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">🚀 When can I start?</span>
            </h3>
            <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span data-i18n="tr">Ön kayıt olun, lansmanımızda hemen başlayabilirsiniz.</span>
              <span data-i18n="en">Pre-register now, you can start immediately at our launch.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section observe-animation" style="background: var(--bg-accent);">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="animate-fade-in-up" style="font-size: var(--font-size-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">
        <span data-i18n="tr">Başka Sorunuz Var mı?</span>
        <span data-i18n="en">Have Other Questions?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="animate-fade-in-up" style="font-size: var(--font-size-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-6); animation-delay: 0.2s; opacity: 0;">
        <span data-i18n="tr">
          Ön kayıt olun, lansmanımızda size özel demo hazırlayalım.
        </span>
        <span data-i18n="en">
          Pre-register and we'll prepare a custom demo for you at launch.
        </span>
      </p>
      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: var(--space-4); flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a class="btn btn-primary hover-glow hover-bounce animate-scale-in" href="/pre-register" style="animation-delay: 0.4s; opacity: 0;">
          <span data-i18n="tr">🚀 Ön Kayıt Ol</span>
          <span data-i18n="en">🚀 Join Waitlist</span>
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary hover-scale animate-scale-in" href="/contact" style="animation-delay: 0.6s; opacity: 0;">
          <span data-i18n="tr">📞 Bize Ulaşın</span>
          <span data-i18n="en">📞 Contact Us</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>